                <span class="article-header-text">Introduction</span><br/>
                <p class="article-text">If you don't know anything about Kanji, this article can provide you with some semblance of basics. Maybe you will even find the read interesting! There are a lot of historical and complicated reasons for why this writing system is the way it is.</p>
